text: Stay safeI know announcing your departure from groups is cringe and unnecessary but I just want to say something  I don t feel in a secure enough place to be on this sub right now  after my most recent attempt I think I just want some space from triggering things   But what I will say to anyone reading this post is wait it out  Please find hope in small things  look at a cool cloud  drink a warm drink  eat something comforting  see someone you love smile  reach out to a friend  even if you haven t spoken in months or years give it a shot  watch a cute cat or dog video  smell fresh bread   I know how much depression makes it hard to see any enjoyment  I love baking but haven t in months because I m just feeling that shit  But still look out for the small things  notice anything that makes you feel emotionally warm  I m not saying it ll make you better but it will give you that   seconds of joy that you can hold on to  Remember there is always more  more good and more bad sure  but you can create good in the most boring situations even by just enjoying the colour of the lamp in your room or some shit   I don t know  I m rambling  just try to stay safe everyone  Hope for better tomorrows  You are important
